CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence signing document, and another on left wearing clerical collar, and two women, including Daisy Lampkin, and Florence Reizenstein on right, gathered around oval table in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
